title: The Origami Bible, by Nick Robinson
description:
This is a new revision, I (accidentally) uploaded it earlier off of unedited .pdf scans.  The scanner didn't get the page size right, so there was a lot of white area around the scans. I've since edited/cropped the book so this is no longer a problem.  It should be a bit smaller now, too...

Note that this book has been a bit of a personal let down, as it claims by the title it's "The Bible" of origami... that leaves a lot to be lived up to, and sorry this book doesn't quite cut it.  It is still a good origami book, but the author should have come up with a different name ;-)
